{"tid":2269901,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"侵侵競選連任主題曲：《票投川普總統》","createTime":"2020-11-03T17:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T06:30:16.000Z","uid":109462,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3b901d96b2cb20256afcb99ffcf9db53cc435a","tid":2269901,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:18:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9TGz4pP593w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9TGz4pP593w&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=7f950df9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9TGz4pP593w</a><br />\nH&atilde;y Bầu cho Tổng Thống Donald Trump: Hợp Ca Hồn Việt<br />\n《票投川普總統》<br />\n演唱：越南靈魂合唱團<br />\n<br />\nUSA！USA！Make America great great again！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c788954dcc347f14ea7bec3129eb2c2959694469","tid":2269901,"uid":109462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"發布精彩視頻 「越南靈魂合唱團」挺川普<br />\n北京時間：2020-11-01 12:55<br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2020年10月31日訊】近日，一個由越裔美國人組成的合唱團發布了其新歌和視頻，用歌聲唱出他們對川普（特朗普）總統的支持。<br />\n<br />\n視頻中的女性穿著飾有美國國旗的傳統越南服裝，該視頻標題為《為川普投票：越南靈魂合唱團》。<br />\n<br />\n越南對美國大選的態度是&mdash;&mdash;川普「勇往直前」。儘管在過去的50年中，美國和中共都在越南的土地上進行過戰爭，但是在很大程度上，這個東南亞國家仍然更擔心「中國威脅」。<br />\n<br />\n政治分析家Linh Nguyen表示，越南的川普粉絲分為兩類：一類是僅僅出於娛樂和個人魅力而喜歡他，另一類是堅決支持川普、並遵循美國政治政策的人，<strong><span class=\"red\">因為他們像香港和台灣的許多人一樣，相信川普是唯一能夠抵抗共產黨的堡壘。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然川普或拜登都沒有闡明他們對越南的戰略，但川普已經明確表示，他不會急於干預其它國家的衝突和爭端。<br />\n<br />\n還有一些人，包括政治活動家Vinh Huu Nguyen認為，只有像川普這樣「勇往之前甚至有些霸道的人」才能真正有所作為。Vinh Huu Nguyen說，這就是川普與之前的領導人不同的地方，與中國打交道需要這種人。<br />\n<br />\nVinh Huu Nguyen表示，<strong><span class=\"red\">只有川普連任，世界才將最終對中國的危脅有清醒的認識。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n與此同時，越南也有擺脫共產黨一黨統治、進行經濟和政治改革的願望。<br />\n<br />\nVinh Huu Nguyen希望，美國對中共的強硬立場能夠對整個共產黨統治地區產生連鎖反應，並最終可以影響到河內（Hanoi）。<br />\n<br />\n（記者李昭希綜合報導/責任編輯：李佳）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/10/31/a102976129.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F10%2F31%2Fa102976129.html&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=d185759b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/10/31/a102976129.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca75c8dc9d14aa6e06f3818e01a81c68a9bf320b","tid":2269901,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"USA！USA！Make America great great again！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df335854822a1872a56f641c3a6317b411b5e7f5","tid":2269901,"uid":64437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FAvFFYu1RGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFAvFFYu1RGM&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b7633481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FAvFFYu1RGM</a><br />\n<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要聽梗係聽呢首啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVote Trump! 2020~"},{"pid":"ce1efe613d1ab3fc404801828c066b54cb325c9b","tid":2269901,"uid":64437,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UwcNlvyx2P4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUwcNlvyx2P4&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4fe16efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UwcNlvyx2P4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bee6f80c629de8f8b9060e32aec7508192e15d","tid":2269901,"uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df335854822a1872a56f641c3a6317b411b5e7f5","tid":2269901,"uid":64437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTim